  "title": "Proper Guitar Holding Techniques",
  "lessonText": "Learn how to hold your guitar correctly for optimal comfort and performance.",
  "data": {
    "content": "- Sit or stand up straight.\n- Hold the guitar close to your body.\n- Use your dominant hand to support the neck.\n- Keep your wrist relaxed and fingers curved.\n- Position the guitar at a comfortable angle."
  }
